{"tid":137200,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京8日走馬看花遊7縣聖巡+紅葉之旅","createTime":"2017-02-27T15:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T10:50:11.000Z","uid":49035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e835bf264bd0436b5626dc427633d35a40b0250","tid":137200,"uid":49035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"上年10月咁啱撞正有紅日又有平機票, 就毒撚一個(大部份時間)走左去東京<br />\n其實2年前已經去過一次東京, 主要都係留市內, 所以今次就比較少時間留喺東京而係走左去其他縣<br />\n有啲景點都可能比較冷門(好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以當係推廣下啲冷門地方 (又或者可能係倒米)<br />\n<br />\n本來plan果陣都唔覺得好chur, 但係一實行就發現時間都幾緊迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩最後都去得完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程如下:<br />\nDay 1 : 成田 --&gt; 東京市內<br />\nDay 2 : 鎌倉+江之島<br />\nDay 3 : 大洗+東京市內<br />\nDay 4 : 宇都宮 --&gt; 大宮 --&gt; 東京 --&gt; 高崎<br />\nDay 5 : 土合+谷川岳<br />\nDay 6 : 長野+志賀高原 --&gt; 東京<br />\nDay 7 : 輕井澤<br />\nDay 8 : 東京市內鳩遊<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 由於我太懶, 所有相都係未經修飾, 影得唔靚唔好怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591ffdb2e1df29d7dee0508c2122083221570445","tid":137200,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7478f8a000705321424df3b287c304a37110d4","tid":137200,"uid":15949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"b2e6a6f03f014621d0471d8fd8f8dad89327313c","tid":137200,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時上水?"},{"pid":"20ea6b09caefa920ff82027fb30e46b1633f6bbe","tid":137200,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"上年10月又去咗東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去咗日光、鐮倉、輕井澤 好撚正<br />\nbtw留名睇遊記"}]}